HEADWORD: Banzai
<hw>Ban"zai"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>interj.</pos> <ety>[Jap.
<ets>banzai</ets>, <ets>banzei</ets>, ten thousand years,
forever.]</ety> <def>Lit., May you live ten thousand years; -- used in
salutation of the emperor and as a battle cry.</def>
